name: startup
description: After interviewing university strudents across several campuses we found that the majority feel      like they don't always know whats happening in the social scene. Turnt solves this problem.      It is a wesbsite/app where people post, share, and save local parties. It alows people to see events      happening near their area, can generate more business for DJ's and small pop up shops, and      eliminates FOMO on college campuses.
